Welcome to the start of Season Six. A new season, with new wrestlers and amazing unscripted combat. A season that promises everything you have come to love and more.
Alexa Von Tess is back after her accident, she is at perfect fighting weight and looks great as a blond. The Badger is taking season six to heart.
Clair Dames is back and will be a regular for season six. With a booming body and amazing tits, we hope she will excel.
Another great match up as the new girl gets dominated and finger at will on the mat. No matter how hard Clair fought "The Badger" got her fingers in and kept them there.
